{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2022/gatsby-hilight-vscode-add/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"88410d89-d5ff-59ba-91f2-e1ccb8d2e6f0","excerpt":"公式 docsに書いてあったのですが、少しわかりにくかったので。 とても簡単に追加できました。 例として .txt と .dart を追加してみます。 対応してる言語 gatsby-remark-vscode は 55 の言語のハイライトに対応してます。(2021/3/11 現在) Batch/CMD Clojure…","html":"<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-vscode/\">公式 docs</a>に書いてあったのですが、少しわかりにくかったので。<br>\nとても簡単に追加できました。</p>\n<p>例として <code>.txt</code> と <code>.dart</code> を追加してみます。</p>\n<h2 id=\"対応してる言語\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AF%BE%E5%BF%9C%E3%81%97%E3%81%A6%E3%82%8B%E8%A8%80%E8%AA%9E\" aria-label=\"対応してる言語 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"display:inline-block; fill:#57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>対応してる言語</h2>\n<p>gatsby-remark-vscode は 55 の言語のハイライトに対応してます。(2021/3/11 現在)</p>\n<details>\n  <summary>一覧(docから引用)</summary>\n<ul>\n<li>Batch/CMD</li>\n<li>Clojure</li>\n<li>CoffeeScript</li>\n<li>C</li>\n<li>C++</li>\n<li>C Platform</li>\n<li>C#</li>\n<li>CSS</li>\n<li>Dockerfile</li>\n<li>F#</li>\n<li>Git Commit</li>\n<li>Git Rebase</li>\n<li>Diff</li>\n<li>Ignore</li>\n<li>Go</li>\n<li>Groovy</li>\n<li>Handlebars</li>\n<li>Hlsl</li>\n<li>HTML</li>\n<li>CSHTML</li>\n<li>PHP HTML</li>\n<li>INI</li>\n<li>Java</li>\n<li>JavaScript</li>\n<li>JSX</li>\n<li>JSON</li>\n<li>JSON with Comments</li>\n<li>Less</li>\n<li>Log</li>\n<li>Lua</li>\n<li>Makefile</li>\n<li>Markdown</li>\n<li>Objective-C</li>\n<li>Objective-C++</li>\n<li>Perl</li>\n<li>Perl 6</li>\n<li>PHP</li>\n<li>Powershell</li>\n<li>Pug</li>\n<li>Python</li>\n<li>R</li>\n<li>Ruby</li>\n<li>Rust</li>\n<li>Sass</li>\n<li>SassDoc</li>\n<li>ShaderLab</li>\n<li>Shell</li>\n<li>SQL</li>\n<li>Swift</li>\n<li>TypeScript</li>\n<li>TSX</li>\n<li>ASP VB .NET</li>\n<li>XML</li>\n<li>XML XSL</li>\n<li>YAML</li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"txt-に対応させる\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#txt-%E3%81%AB%E5%AF%BE%E5%BF%9C%E3%81%95%E3%81%9B%E3%82%8B\" aria-label=\"txt に対応させる permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"display:inline-block; fill:#57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.txt に対応させる</h2>\n<p>これは対応というかエイリアスを設定します。<br>\n<code>gatsby-config.js</code> にて <code>ignore</code> にすれば期待通りになる。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"jsx\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  resolve: </span><span class=\"mtk8\">`gatsby-remark-vscode`</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    options: {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      languageAliases: { txt: </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;ignore&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> },</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    },</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">},</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"dart-に対応させる\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dart-%E3%81%AB%E5%AF%BE%E5%BF%9C%E3%81%95%E3%81%9B%E3%82%8B\" aria-label=\"dart に対応させる permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"display:inline-block; fill:#57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.dart に対応させる</h2>\n<p>まず、VSCode にて Dart 言語のプラグインを表示させます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ec2ff263d9e4bfcccb4c5ce13bac1851/c02c7/screenshot_dart_vsc.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.736842105263165%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"vscode-dart-extension\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ec2ff263d9e4bfcccb4c5ce13bac1851/3c051/screenshot_dart_vsc.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ec2ff263d9e4bfcccb4c5ce13bac1851/a2d4f/screenshot_dart_vsc.png 190w,\n/static/ec2ff263d9e4bfcccb4c5ce13bac1851/3f520/screenshot_dart_vsc.png 380w,\n/static/ec2ff263d9e4bfcccb4c5ce13bac1851/3c051/screenshot_dart_vsc.png 760w,\n/static/ec2ff263d9e4bfcccb4c5ce13bac1851/b5cea/screenshot_dart_vsc.png 1140w,\n/static/ec2ff263d9e4bfcccb4c5ce13bac1851/891d5/screenshot_dart_vsc.png 1520w,\n/static/ec2ff263d9e4bfcccb4c5ce13bac1851/c02c7/screenshot_dart_vsc.png 2472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>リソースのところにリポジトリとあるのでリクックしてブラウザで開きます。(上画像赤丸)</p>\n<p>リポジトリのリンクは <code>https://github.com/Dart-Code/Dart-Code</code> なので npm で次のようにインストールします。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">$ npm i Dart-Code/Dart-Code</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>package.json</code> の <code>name</code> プロパティを確認して、</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/33a9dfb059b24764289712a6512eb10b/3d405/screenshot_dart_pkg.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.84210526315789%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"dart-code\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/33a9dfb059b24764289712a6512eb10b/3c051/screenshot_dart_pkg.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/33a9dfb059b24764289712a6512eb10b/a2d4f/screenshot_dart_pkg.png 190w,\n/static/33a9dfb059b24764289712a6512eb10b/3f520/screenshot_dart_pkg.png 380w,\n/static/33a9dfb059b24764289712a6512eb10b/3c051/screenshot_dart_pkg.png 760w,\n/static/33a9dfb059b24764289712a6512eb10b/b5cea/screenshot_dart_pkg.png 1140w,\n/static/33a9dfb059b24764289712a6512eb10b/3d405/screenshot_dart_pkg.png 1348w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code>gatsby-config.js</code> に以下のように <code>extensions</code> プロパティに書きます。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"jsx\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  resolve: </span><span class=\"mtk8\">`gatsby-remark-vscode`</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    options: {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      extensions: [</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;dart-code&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">],</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    },</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">},</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>これで対応終了です。</p>\n<p><code>.txt</code> も vscode プラグインで何かあるなら、エイリアスを貼るのではなく <code>.dart</code> の時と同じような手順で対応するのも良いと思う。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83\" aria-label=\"参考 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"display:inline-block; fill:#57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参考</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/andrewbranch/gatsby-remark-vscode/issues/130\">https://github.com/andrewbranch/gatsby-remark-vscode/issues/130</a></p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n  .default-dark {\n    background-color: #1E1E1E;\n    color: #D4D4D4;\n  }\n  .default-dark .mtk1 { color: #D4D4D4; }\n  .default-dark .mtk8 { color: #CE9178; }\n  .default-dark .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));\n  }\n</style>","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022/gatsby-hilight-vscode-add/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gatsby-remark-vscodeにハイライト可能な言語を追加する","description":null,"postdate":"2022-03-11T19:13:00","update":"2022-03-11T19:13:00","tags":["Gatsby"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022/gatsby-site-create-log9/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"9.細かい変更 (Gatsby-jsによるサイト構築記録)"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022/gatsby-site-create-log10/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"10.Github Pagesでデプロイとアナリティクスとサイトマップ (Gatsby-jsによるサイト構築記録)"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"88410d89-d5ff-59ba-91f2-e1ccb8d2e6f0","previousPostId":"9af82e1d-4bd4-5d30-bbe2-a591f5f126d8","nextPostId":"a0a97e7a-803f-55e7-a49e-f3127c234fa3"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3405293526","713408048"],"slicesMap":{}}